name: Erin
description: FLOWER POP: This collection is based on taking my floral cell phone photography and making pop art out of them.  I love the style of Pop Art with the Splashes of Color. What perfect subject than flowers. I have named each image a human name because why the heck not. Honestly, I named each flower the first name that POPPED into my head.  This is Erin, meet Erin! Thank you!
